Darwin's Nightmare;;87;;90;;NC;;Hubert Sauper's Oscar-nominated documentary about the Nile perch, a species introduced into Lake Victoria as an experiment in the sixties. Since then, the fish has not only wiped out the lake's other marine life, but also has a tendency to consume its own young. Unfortunately, the Nile perch is also the region's most profitable export. Everyone with a stake in the market downplays the ecological disaster.;;Documentary;;Hubert Sauper;;2005;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1159353-darwins_nightmare